               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Gadla Takla Hāymānot “Vita of Takla Haymanot” (fols. 4ra-149ra)&#xD;
                     II) Maṣḥafa lǝdätu la-ʾabuna Takla Hāymānot “Book of the Genealogy of ʾabuna
                     Takla Haymanot” (fols. 149ra-151vb)&#xD; - Genealogy of Takla Hāymānot (fols.
                     149ra-150rb)&#xD; - Wa-nabara ʾabbā Yoḥanni ba-Dabra Dāmmo... “And ʾabbā
                     Yoḥanni lived in Dabra Dāmmo...” (fol. 150rb-vb)&#xD; - Zenā mänakosat “The
                     Story of the Monks” (fols. 150vb-151vb)&#xD; &#xD; Additiones 1-4.</summary>
